      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical R2022 R2 and FDA in-house FEA code are both under formal SQA plans with documented version control, issue tracking, and release validation testing.",
      "rationale": "All three modeling environments (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented SQA procedures. Version-controlled input decks and archived solver binaries ensure reproducibility. Gradation 2 achieved and required for Medium model risk."
