      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario (ASTM F1717 compression-bending) is the same scenario as the COU; no extrapolation required.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity is co-extensive with the COU: both concern ASTM F1717 static compression-bending of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. No extrapolation in geometry, loading mode, or material is required. The validation directly supports the COU without interpolation or analogy arguments."
